WEBVTT

00:08:28.200 --> 00:08:31.176
In fact, we're all
hallucinating all the time,

00:08:31.200 --> 00:08:32.576
including right now.

00:08:32.600 --> 00:08:35.416
It's just that when we agree
about our hallucinations,

00:08:35.440 --> 00:08:36.640
we call that reality.

00:08:37.280 --> 00:08:41.216
(Laughter)

00:08:41.240 --> 00:08:44.576
Now I'm going to tell you
that your experience of being a self,

00:08:44.600 --> 00:08:46.416
the specific experience of being you,

00:08:46.440 --> 00:08:49.936
is also a controlled hallucination
generated by the brain.

00:08:49.960 --> 00:08:51.976
This seems a very strange idea, right?

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:54.136
Yes, visual illusions
might deceive my eyes,

00:08:54.160 --> 00:08:57.680
but how could I be deceived
about what it means to be me?

00:08:58.200 --> 00:08:59.416
For most of us,

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.016
the experience of being a person